This is bad, I thought he knew!

9
00:00:35,690 --> 00:00:37,710
Why is Takaya in my house?

10
00:00:37,710 --> 00:00:40,130
You've got it all wrong!

11
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:43,030
I was looking for a lawyer to settle my divorce

12
00:00:43,030 --> 00:00:45,790
and Takaya came to mind,

13
00:00:45,790 --> 00:00:47,850
so I gave him a call

14
00:00:47,850 --> 00:00:50,320
and asked for another lawyer in his firm.

15
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:53,170
Another lawyer to take up my case.

16
00:00:53,170 --> 00:00:56,940
And voila, he came in person anyway.

17
00:00:56,940 --> 00:01:00,480
I'm sorry, I wanted to meet Midori again after such a long time.

18
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:02,950
But I didn't know this was Saki's...

19
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:06,290
That this is Saki's love nest.

20
00:01:06,290 --> 00:01:08,480
I just assumed it was the home of a friend of yours.

21
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:12,490
Now that you mentioned, I'm sorry I didn't explain it to you properly.

22
00:01:17,270 --> 00:01:21,330
What's the relationship between you both?

23
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:23,850
Koichi was my...

24
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:25,640
Aoyama was my...

25
00:01:26,340 --> 00:01:28,260
We knew each other at the gym we used to frequent.

26
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:31,610
What a coincidence. Didn't know such things can happen.

27
00:01:32,870 --> 00:01:35,050
I really didn't know about it.

28
