I'm sorry.

29
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:43,420
You didn't know about it.

30
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:47,350
No worries.

31
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:50,340
You need not apologize.

32
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,900
Then I'll get going.

33
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,400
- Are you leaving already?
- Midori, regarding the case...

34
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,980
We'll discuss it next time.

35
00:01:56,980 --> 00:01:59,470
Well, we've cleared up the misunderstanding already, so it's all right.

36
00:01:59,470 --> 00:02:02,760
- It's been a while since you met Saki too, right?
- Actually, no. Recently-

37
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:07,560
Recently?

38
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,000
It was a coincidence. A coincidence!

39
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,480
We bumped into each other at a restaurant. It's really a coincidence!

40
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:14,320
That's right! We bumped into each other at a restaurant we used to frequent.

41
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,960
It was really a coincidence.

42
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,510
I'll take my leave then.

43
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:42,820
Hey, why don't you have some cheesecake that Takaya bought?

44
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:44,650
It's really delicious.

45
00:02:44,650 --> 00:02:45,820
Right, Azusa?

46
00:02:45,820 --> 00:02:47,580
- Where are you going?
- That's right, that's right!

47
00:02:47,580 --> 00:02:50,550
It's really delicious.

48
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:52,020
"My, how lovely!"

49
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:54,180
Was what you thought I would say?

50
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:56,370
Must you get so angry?

51
00:02:56,370 --> 00:02:59,090
Anyway, the both of you should leave!

52
00:02:59,090 --> 00:03:00,930
You have a home to return to, don't you, Mom?

53
00:03:00,930 --> 00:03:03,240
If you don't want to, just...  stay over at a hotel!

54
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,700
I know already. Let me get my luggage. My luggage!

55
00:03:05,700 --> 00:03:08,750
All right, all right. I've got the luggage.
<i>[Honeymoon Air Tickets]</i>

56
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:10,690
Let's wear our shoes.

57
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:13,210
Hurry up!

58
00:03:18,650 --> 00:03:20,260
Well...

59
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,450
I'm sorry!

60
00:03:22,450 --> 00:03:24,030
About what?

61
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:27,750
My mom just acted without asking.

62
00:03:28,570 --> 00:03:31,730
But please, believe me. He...

63
00:03:31,730 --> 00:03:35,040
Aoyama and I met each other out of pure coincidence. We-

64
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:38,000
- You need not explain it to me.
- But...

65
00:03:38,940 --> 00:03:40,950
We are...

66
