67
00:03:44,210 --> 00:03:45,850
It's great timing too.

68
00:03:45,850 --> 00:03:48,110
You can discuss it with your ex-boyfriend.

69
00:03:48,110 --> 00:03:50,350
How can you...

70
00:03:50,350 --> 00:03:52,980
And are you all right with that, Koichi?

71
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:54,800
No problem at all.

72
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:08,980
<i>My longest relationship was with my ex-girlfriend, whom I split with four months ago.</i>

73
00:04:08,980 --> 00:04:11,660
<i>She got married, out of spite,</i>

74
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:13,240
<i>with a guy she had just met.</i>

75
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,790
<i>It could have been anyone, right?</i>

76
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:45,550
<i>We became so close together.</i>

77
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:48,730
<i>Even then...</i>

78
00:04:48,730 --> 00:04:51,470
<i>Ex-Ex-boyfriend?</i>

79
00:04:52,890 --> 00:04:56,540
<i>You met each other, recently?</i>

80
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:01,340
<i>He has misunderstood me.</i>

81
